description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 moving puzzles are included.
-Chihuahua Puppy
-Five French Bulldog Puppies
-Labrador Retriever Puppy
-Two Siberian Husky Puppies
-Maltipoo Puppy
-Jack Russell Terrier Puppy
-Golden Retriever Puppy
-Four Japanese Spitz Puppies
-Maltese Puppy
-Pomeranian Puppy
name: [Moving] Fluffy Puppies
